Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟之国的任务已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样的话 鸣人怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是我这个队长的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者的任务往往伴随牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 回村吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为他们真的会回去吗 流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是比较在意那个带面罩的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我去跟踪他们吗 北辰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用 还是我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回去汇报一下情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人之死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,余下二人以及后来赶来汇合的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经出了国境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该在回木叶村的路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入大名府的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已经被鹭大人处决了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好茶好茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮家伙从刚才开始到底在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是柿子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:03:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替身术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶的忍者们居然敢欺骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红明大人 请出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟之国 谋士红明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滥用国家谋士之权
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀前代大名以及公主朱鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且派遣部下装扮成诅咒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专横跋扈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛊惑人心 干涉朝政
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此等危及鹭大人大名之位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,篡位害人之罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天地难容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 赐你切腹自刎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此啊 是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,申子绪 你居然陷害我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丢脸啊 红明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武士就该有气魄以死谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即执行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是雾隐之术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管这些 赶快杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上路吧 对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就是诅咒武士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们继续追
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先行一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事需要调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们果然是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是那天晚上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽灵的真面目 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵诅咒武士的就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是为了调查诅咒武士而去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那位大人会这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不见棺材不掉泪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我来揭穿你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您刚才到那儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下再解释吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们赶快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 你们也跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 天天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直跟踪我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你不想出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通灵之术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙找出隐藏在这里的忍者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 躲在这边的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉迷藏的游戏到此为止了 快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗鼻子果然与众不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来躲不了了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总算肯现身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里怎么会有这样的地道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说大名为了能了解庶民们的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而开凿了这条遍布全国范围的地道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说诅咒武士和大名有关咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不会是幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在过会儿 对方应该会自表身份的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,返回村子应该是被雇佣忍者们的常识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务的初衷既然变了 那就另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的任务疑点太多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们过于干涉别国的内政了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不像狗一样乱闻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来应该可以活着回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉 狗招你惹你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森罗万象 防护之术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道身体里含有岩石的成份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然已经知道这个国家的秘密了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能让你们活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像比较麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.70,0:11:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的我一个人能够应付
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 那我先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬化 岩石战车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引爆符
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里应该可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣…鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒武士的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是鹭大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…你到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鹭大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是鹭大人做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那个站姿来看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确定就是鹭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实情况比较复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干吗啊 天天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么不早点告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很早就知道是鸣人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么能这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直有忍者在监视我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次 天天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加快步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被人跟踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在返回鸟之国
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别被发现了 就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是用替身把那人甩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可那只是暂时性的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刑场追诅咒武士开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个人又跟了上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我一个人知情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是白提你们操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是你代替鹭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那鹭大人平安无事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们担心了 哪个可恶的申子绪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严刑拷打逼我认罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 你受了很多罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来龙去脉 进去以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹭大哥等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬化 岩吹雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们流浪忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有归属之地 四处辗转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷学各村忍术精髓 创造属于自己的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说这招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写轮眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬化 砂缚枢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 居然连我爱罗的忍术也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬化 砂瀑送葬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹭大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千岛大哥情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有生命危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在我府邸的医疗室接受治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在休息当中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千岛他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁…是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,误会你了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小人实在承受不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.90,0:17:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是千岛他拼了命前来告诉我实情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今却不能让知道一切的你活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私闯大名府 你已经是死罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是飞镖所伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快去御医那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹭大人 请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:17:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,申子绪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 申子绪背叛了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀你父亲和妹妹的也是他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他指派自己的亲信忍者使用近卫兵的飞镖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的是嫁祸给红明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是被申子绪给暗算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撑住啊 千岛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹭大人 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快停止红明大人的处刑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不去就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以停止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让申子绪发现我已经知道真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法复仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你为了复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜牺牲任何人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红明被申子绪的心腹看守着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是贸然出手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们更本没有任何胜算
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:18:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人去救红明大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你该没意见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我就假扮了诅咒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己扮成诅咒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为的是寻找暗杀父亲的真凶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是非但没有找到凶手 红明…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而却成了陷害你的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直觉得那天的诅咒武士就是您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才去了诅咒武士一度消失的寺庙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就遇到了诅咒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个诅咒武士并不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是申子绪叫人伪装的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都明了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是申子绪那个老头搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,申子绪这个老匹夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道想先除了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再谋害鹭大人篡位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个老头居然还假惺惺的装好人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想揍他一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人还有各位 辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始 一切都交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我一个人去了结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心中的表
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然只会停留在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.51,0:22:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人能干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你想复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可人死不能复生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.44,0:22:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此 你还执着于复仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做能让你快乐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.44,0:22:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:23:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父亲和妹妹真的会高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.40,0:23:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静止的时间
